# Normalize line endings so the working tree matches CI (Linux, LF).
# Without this, Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) materialize CRLF files,
# which makes `npm run format:check` (Prettier endOfLine: lf) fail locally even
# though CI is green. Pinning eol=lf keeps format/lint reproducible on every OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Build/library artifacts that must stay untouched
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg text eol=lf
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
